data.description: Welcome to your charming retreat! Nestled in the perfect location, just off 495 and close to FedEx Field and major shopping centers, this lovely townhome offers convenience and style in one delightful package.  With new carpet & paint this home exudes a welcoming atmosphere with hardwood flooring throughout the main level. This house offers a gourmet kitchen, beautiful granite counters, stainless steel appliances, and a large deck just off the kitchen, overlooking the fully fenced backyard. The spacious bedrooms provide comfort and versatility, ensuring ample space for relaxation or a home office setup. The thoughtful design of this home maximizes both functionality and aesthetic appeal. Step outside and unwind on the spacious front porch, perfect for enjoying a quiet evening or greeting neighbors in this friendly community.  Convenience is key, with easy access to major highways and proximity to FedEx Field and renowned shopping destinations.  Please note that no Home Warranty is available for this property. The seller prefers the use of Home First Title, streamlining the closing process for your convenience.   Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to make 7808 Suiter Lane your home. Schedule a showing today and discover the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience in this delightful townhome. $295 co-broke charge charged to buyer brokerage.
